high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the trash can.
Take the apple out of the trash can.
Go to the fridge on your left.
Put the apple in the fridge, then take the apple out of the fridge.
Go back to the trash can on your right.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away an apple that you put in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the trash can next to the fridge.
Pick up the apple from the trash can.
Bring the apple to the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge.
Bring the apple to the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the short walk trashcan next to the fridge.
Remove the green apple from the short white trashcan.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the apple in front of the coffee mug then close the door, after a few seconds open the fridge door back up and remove the green apple.
Turn right and walk back over to the short white trashcan.
Place the chilled green apple back inside the short white trashcan.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled green apple inside a short white trashcan.
